Dependencies and requirements (summary):
- Python 3.11 environment (see requirements_mac_311.txt / requirements_windows_311.txt)
- FastAPI application stack (installed via requirements files)
- ffmpeg installed separately and available on PATH for audio features (not bundled)
- Local LLM model files in GGUF format (downloaded from official model repositories; not included)
- Optional: fastmcp (only required to run the MCP demo server in lai/tools/micro mcp server/)

Notes:
- Model files are not shipped with this repository; place them under models/.
- Some features rely on external binaries or local system capabilities (e.g., ffmpeg).
